.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Rules you must follow</h2>\n\n<p>When you&rsquo;re registered under <abbr title=\"Construction Industry Scheme\">CIS</abbr>, you must:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/what-you-must-do-as-a-cis-contractor/verifying-and-paying-your-subcontractors\" title=\"verifying and paying your subcontractors\">check with <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr></a> that your subcontractors are registered under <abbr title=\"Construction Industry Scheme\">CIS</abbr> </li>\n  <li>make the right <abbr title=\"Construction Industry Scheme\">CIS</abbr> deductions (tax and National Insurance) to payments you make to your subcontractors </li>\n  <li><a href=\"/what-you-must-do-as-a-cis-contractor/pay-cis-deductions-to-hmrc\" title=\"pay CIS deductions\">pay <abbr title=\"Construction Industry Scheme\">CIS</abbr> deductions</a> to <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> </li>\n  <li><a href=\"/what-you-must-do-as-a-cis-contractor/file-your-monthly-returns\" title=\"file monthly returns\">file monthly returns</a> with <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> </li>\n  <li>keep full <a href=\"/what-you-must-do-as-a-cis-contractor/record-keeping\" title=\"record keeping\"><abbr title=\"Construction Industry Scheme\">CIS</abbr> records</a> </li>\n  <li>let <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> know about any <a href=\"/what-you-must-do-as-a-cis-contractor/tell-hmrc-about-changes\" title=\"changes to your status\">changes to your status</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/what-you-must-do-as-a-cis-contractor/verifying-and-paying-your-subcontractors","slug":"verifying-and-paying-your-subcontractors","order":2,"title":"Verifying and paying your subcontractors","body":"<p>Before paying your subcontractors you must check their employment status - you can do this with the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/calcs/esi.htm\" title=\"employment status tool\">employment status tool</a> on the HM Revenu