ur return is but they range from £100 to £3,000 or the total amount of <abbr title=\"Construction Industry Scheme\">CIS</abbr> deductions shown on your late return - whichever is higher.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>There’s more information about <a href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/cis/returns/late-return-pen.htm\" title=\"penalties for late returns\" rel=\"external\">penalties for late returns</a> on the <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> website.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Correcting or amending returns</h2>\n\n<p>If you make a mistake, you might need to contact <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> - there&rsquo;s more information about this on the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/cis/returns/correct-return.htm\" title=\"HMRC website\"><abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> website.</a> </p>\n\n<p>You can also change something in your return if you need to. To correct a mistake or change something, call the <abbr title=\"Construction Industry Scheme\">CIS</abbr> helpline:</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"Construction Industry Scheme\">CIS</abbr> helpline</strong><br />\n0845 366 7899<br />\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 8pm<br />\nSaturday, 8am to 4pm</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You can also write to <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> at the address below.</p>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\n<abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr>  \n<br />Custom House  \n<br />Carnbane Way  \n<br />Carnbane Industrial Estate  \n<br />Newry\n<br />BT35 6QG \n<br />\n</p></div></div>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/what-you-must-do-as-a-cis-contractor/record-keeping","slug":"record-keeping","order":5,"title":"Record keeping","body":"<p>Under the Construction Industry Scheme (<abbr title=\"Construction Industry Scheme\">CIS</abbr>), you must keep records of:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the gross amount of each payment made to each subcontr